Name: ChibiTama
About the game: 'ChibiTama' is a game that combines elements of shooting and tower defense. Players will encounter many stages, variety of enemies, and big bosses! Deploy your players and supporters, and band together to survive the stages! As you do so, your characters will grow! Little cute characters are waiting for you! Stay tuned for more features and characters to be added soon!
